PROJECT STRUCTURE

1. CREATE NEW BRANCH PER FEATURE

    1.1 Example:
            feature/battle-chat
    1.2 Push to develop after completion

2. CREATE NEW PACKAGE PER FEATURE

    2.1 Example:
            atlas.com.trainerapp
            |---authentication
                |---models
                |---views
                |---presenter/controller

    2.2 General use class will be placed in root
            atlas.com.trainerapp
            |---widgets
            |---utils
            |---firebase
3. GUIDE FOR NAMING XML ELEMENTS

    3.1
        EditText        : et_
        TextView        : tv_
        LinearLayout    : ll_
        ..
        etc